about your own face, right?

139
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:20,279
That's because the whole situation

140
00:07:20,279 --> 00:07:22,000
was already under my control.

141
00:07:24,279 --> 00:07:25,519
Dongfang Chen.

142
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:27,680
You're more than just a face.

143
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,639
You're also

144
00:07:29,639 --> 00:07:32,439
brave and genuine.

145
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,160
Of course,

146
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,959
